{"tid":2095502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（鼠疫大爆發！）內蒙古驚傳「腺鼠疫」！緊急發3級警告","createTime":"2020-07-05T13:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:08:14.000Z","uid":66087,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"34a84e734b0e31a5313bb9d93baab8aa12e46273","tid":2095502,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"內蒙古驚傳「腺鼠疫」！緊急發3級警告<br />\n<br />\n記者趙蔡州／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n大陸內蒙古巴彥淖爾市傳出有民眾感染鼠疫。《人民日報》報導，烏拉特中旗7月4日通報有1人疑似感染腺鼠疫病例，當地政府考量後決定發布「鼠疫防控3級預警」，2020年7月5日起正式進入預警期，預警時間為通告發布後持續到2020年底。<br />\n<br />\n巴彥淖爾市衛生健康委員會表示，民眾在預警期間發現病（死）動物務必通報、發現疑似鼠疫病人要通報、發現不明原因的發燒病人和急病死者要通報，進入鼠疫疫源地務必謹慎，如有鼠疫疫源地的旅居史，出現發燒等不適症狀時，務必及時到指定醫院就診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 快訊／內蒙古驚傳「腺鼠疫」！緊急發3級警告 急病死亡全要通報ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200705/1753369.htm#ixzz6RKJHB8ry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200705%2F1753369.htm%23ixzz6RKJHB8ry&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj34429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=4004b7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200705/1753369.htm#ixzz6RKJHB8ry</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"759286ffb7a9f66cb8ad9c4b169c24a5461c4850","tid":2095502,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"內蒙鼠疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4502df9b6177f7bc53a0cd5869a0107e7eb45841","tid":2095502,"uid":108359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"食哂d老鼠咪冇事 又贏"},{"pid":"486cb1569281b26d6df866dee46a402f63398d57","tid":2095502,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"講左咁多個月都無事, <br />\n點會有事, 信黨無事"},{"pid":"37908247ccc47dac198e9b9df6c77f60102e991f","tid":2095502,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"有冇多難興邦bingo紙"},{"pid":"7601a60ad553d16af81d